{"tid":1165874,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"佛祖頭？Galaxy Note 10 渲染圖揭穿孔鏡頭置中設計","createTime":"2019-05-22T05:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T03:26:41.000Z","uid":159448,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"2390d87c556ce3d4bf6f1ab61681e24c14a4b141","tid":1165874,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:26:46.000Z","msg":"在智能手機市場上，穿孔、瀏海、水滴等全面屏都已經成為司空見慣。而近日，外國知名爆料人士指出，Samsung Galaxy Note 10 或採用前所未有的屏幕打孔設計，將打孔移到屏幕中間。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rhz6eir.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRhz6eir.jpg&h=e0f23437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據 PhoneArena 最新消息，在 Samsung Galaxy Note 10 渲染圖中，手機採用對稱式設計，無論是正面還是背部，前置開孔鏡頭和後置鏡頭都將置中對稱。屏幕開孔位置與原本的開孔方式都有不同，採用中間穿孔的設計，而且後置也改為垂直排列。目前，前置中間鏡頭有單鏡頭和雙鏡頭兩個版本，不排除對應 Galaxy Note 10 兩種機型的可能。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QJ1cUis.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQJ1cUis.png&h=de6d0772&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前消息指出，Galaxy Note 10 將會採用 19:9 比例的超感官全視屏，採用 Snapdragon 855 處理器，記憶體體及儲存方面最高會有 12GB + 1TB 的組合，4,170mAh 電池容量，支援 25W 快充。鏡頭方面， Galaxy Note 10 採用可變光圈主鏡頭+超廣角+光學變焦後置三鏡頭組合設計，而 Galaxy Note 10 Pro 則會增加一顆 ToF 鏡頭。 Samsung 預計最快會在  8月發布 Galaxy Note 10 系列旗艦手機，讓我們拭目以待吧。<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2019/05/22/samsung-galaxy-note-10-pro-design-camera-leaked/?fbclid=IwAR3qs1TkHqjk52y95cnPs9HzD6vlOFcNxP85EybdICQkb_U9AkUO4UK6ukA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2019%2F05%2F22%2Fsamsung-galaxy-note-10-pro-design-camera-leaked%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3qs1TkHqjk52y95cnPs9HzD6vlOFcNxP85EybdICQkb_U9AkUO4UK6ukA&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=4d48b232\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2019/05/22/samsung-galaxy-note-10-pro-design-camera-leaked/?fbclid=IwAR3qs1TkHqjk52y95cnPs9HzD6vlOFcNxP85EybdICQkb_U9AkUO4UK6ukA</a>"},{"pid":"16ee75d445a348a3671732ddf270480f5bfd0edd","tid":1165874,"uid":22675,"like":28,"dislike":6,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:28:00.000Z","msg":"不如直接取消個前鏡頭仲好啦"},{"pid":"77f7e1a38a5459e4e1ddf9f5540637a4ef21d1d7","tid":1165874,"uid":254259,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:29:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83fa1c2b5b50a3e10ff78ed3b8550c656d7e48b8","tid":1165874,"uid":109923,"like":18,"dislike":10,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:37:43.000Z","msg":"柒過m額<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尤其雙鏡頭"},{"pid":"d27097c541267ad90b0ee20fa85f1ddc6d474939","tid":1165874,"uid":1888,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:49:13.000Z","msg":"好柒呀"},{"pid":"f1675713eb8eff9c5dde1e991e238c1da9197b5d","tid":1165874,"uid":33653,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:53:40.000Z","msg":"用幻視/家燕姐做wallpaper 岩曬"},{"pid":"85fff2db3fcfc7ccd1663f9a4f5977bd6acd95a0","tid":1165874,"uid":159448,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83fa1c2b5b50a3e10ff78ed3b8550c656d7e48b8","tid":1165874,"uid":109923,"like":18,"dislike":10,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:37:43.000Z","msg":"柒過m額<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尤其雙鏡頭"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T09:14:44.000Z","msg":"前鏡真係無需要雙鏡 一個廣角咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a1a2c017af65ecea5c23dad5186d8de9f83e71","tid":1165874,"uid":51294,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"85fff2db3fcfc7ccd1663f9a4f5977bd6acd95a0","tid":1165874,"uid":159448,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83fa1c2b5b50a3e10ff78ed3b8550c656d7e48b8","tid":1165874,"uid":109923,"like":18,"dislike":10,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:37:43.000Z","msg":"柒過m額<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尤其雙鏡頭"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T09:14:44.000Z","msg":"前鏡真係無需要雙鏡 一個廣角咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji